des: You can use this skill to find out a bit more about Rob Levin. If you're interested in interviewing me but you simply can't wait, my Alexa skill will answer common interview questions like, "tell me about yourself", "what's your biggest accomplishment", or "what's the most difficult situation you've faced".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
